3.00	Chunghwa_Post	Chunghwa Post	The Chunghwa Post Co., Ltd. (Chinese: ), from 2007 to 08 Taiwan Post Co. (台灣郵政), is the official postal service of the Republic of China (ROC), providing mail service for Free Area of the Republic of China, which covers Taiwan, Kinmen, Matsu, Pratas and Itu Aba. It also provides a savings account service. Chunghwa Post was a government organization of Ministry of Transportation and Communications until 2003, when it was reorganized into a government-owned corporation.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/52/Miaoli_Mail.JPG/220px-Miaoli_Mail.JPG
